          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Each new iteration from Draknek & Friends brings forth a slew of new ideas, new mechanics and more devious challenges to overcome. Thankfully, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
