            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " doesn’t disappoint and has around 200 puzzles to sink one’s teeth into. Now sit back and grab your things, we’re going to burn them... yes that’s right, you heard me correctly!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
